oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Jimmy Dickens Press Release: Version 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Dickens, Little Jimmy, 1920-2015; Moeller Talent, Inc.; Offset printing;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: A black and white negative taped to and framed by a masking sheet advertising Jimmy Dickens and containing a biography of his life and accomplishments. The press release describes his childhood, early music career, Grand Ole Opry membership, world tour, television shows he appeared on, songs recorded, and hobbies. The photograph of Jimmy Dickens is missing. This version of the press release is the same as version three, except it has the Moeller Talent, Inc. address. The negative would have been used to create a corresponding printing plate.
